nature_of_business: Leschaco is a leading international provider of integrated logistic services company which caters for all types of logistics support by tailored its own services to suit the precise requirements of each individual customer. AIRFREIGHT: - Leschaco links your goods to the remotest corners of the world with flexibility and efficiency air transport solutions within our global network. - IATA Transport/Refigerated Goods/Express Traffic/Plant & Projects. ISO TANK CONTAINER - We are the pioneers for tank container logistics in overseas transportation offering gapless door-to-door traffic, including the use of the optimal carrier for initial and terminal haulage, custom clearance and related document management within our own network worldwide. PROJECT LOGISTICS: - Leschaco's customer oriented international project teams tailored the entire logistics solutions to move your complex & large scale industrial plant to your specified destination to ensure your project success. DISTRIBUTION LOGISTICS: - Leschaco offers facility/warehouse solutions to administer cargoes of individual customers. - warehousing, Order Picking & Distribution. name: INTEGRA PETROCHEMICALS PTE LTD
nature_of_business: Integra has grown to become one of the world's leading petrochemical traders & logistics companies with headquarters in Singapore and offices in the major trading hubs worldwide. Since its formation in Europe in 1989, Integra has developed from its origins as one of the early olefins trading companies into a global company handling a wide range of petrochemicals gases and aromatics and petrochemical liquids. Integra has a longstanding presence in both established and emerging markets, with offices in Singapore, Houston, Brussels, Riyadh, Delhi, Seoul and Beijing. The companys ship owning arm is based in Singapore with a fleet of 15 chemical carriers. Integra offers a unique combination of technical skills with specialist logistical experience to provide a complete service to customers, from sourcing and acquiring products to transporting and delivering them safely. Integra particularly prides itself on its strong relationships with customers, and these remain the priority at the heart of its approach to business (www.integra-global.com).
